snippet.title: Chior Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3175040/Chior/

You had a pretty rough fall. Trying to regain your composure you try to look around before realizing you can't see anything. Hope that your other senses will serve you better.
